<br />
FP - You could Start with Haldir and Arwen, and pull Leggy - but whatever.<br />
<br />
Galadriel and Elrond are there to keep Leggy alive...incase he gets jacked.  Use Leggy as primary fighter - which is what the events are for as well as conditions.<br />
<br />
3 is my lucky number.  I&#39;ve considered adding in Balglin - he&#39;s hard to kill - and with strength base five, is easily overwhelmed unless you have good support.<br />
<br />
No Burden Removal - but you have Liberation.<br />
<br />
Shadow, I&#39;m trying to work it out to where you can stop your opponent, but keep your minions alive and well.  Which is why Not Easily Destroyed, all Blades Perish and Wreathed in Shadow are there...<br />
<br />
Don&#39;t count on winning with the minions, the minions are meant to slow down your opponent and hlep your own FP along.<br />
<br />
DRAWING/Discarding - Fell Beast, Elven Sword and Gwemegil - all meant to be used to fullest extent - so you can draw more cards at the regroup...<br />
<br />
